9#ifndef SAE_H
10#define SAE_H
11
12#define SAE_KCK_LEN 32
13#define SAE_PMK_LEN 32
14#define SAE_PMKID_LEN 16
15#define SAE_KEYSEED_KEY_LEN 32
16#define SAE_MAX_PRIME_LEN 512
17#define SAE_MAX_ECC_PRIME_LEN 66
18#define SAE_COMMIT_MAX_LEN (2 + 3 * SAE_MAX_PRIME_LEN)
19#define SAE_CONFIRM_MAX_LEN (2 + SAE_MAX_PRIME_LEN)
20
21/* Special value returned by sae_parse_commit() */
22#define SAE_SILENTLY_DISCARD 65535
23
24struct sae_temporary_data {
25 u8 kck[SAE_KCK_LEN];
26 struct crypto_bignum *own_commit_scalar;
27 struct crypto_bignum *own_commit_element_ffc;
28 struct crypto_ec_point *own_commit_element_ecc;
29 struct crypto_bignum *peer_commit_element_ffc;
30 struct crypto_ec_point *peer_commit_element_ecc;
31 struct crypto_ec_point *pwe_ecc;
32 struct crypto_bignum *pwe_ffc;
33 struct crypto_bignum *sae_rand;
34 struct crypto_ec *ec;
35 int prime_len;
36 const struct dh_group *dh;
37 const struct crypto_bignum *prime;
38 const struct crypto_bignum *order;
39 struct crypto_bignum *prime_buf;
40 struct crypto_bignum *order_buf;
41 struct wpabuf *anti_clogging_token;
42 char *pw_id;
43};
44
45enum sae_state {
46 SAE_NOTHING, SAE_COMMITTED, SAE_CONFIRMED, SAE_ACCEPTED
47};
48
49struct sae_data {
50 enum sae_state state;
51 u16 send_confirm;
52 u8 pmk[SAE_PMK_LEN];
53 u8 pmkid[SAE_PMKID_LEN];
54 struct crypto_bignum *peer_commit_scalar;
55 int group;
56 unsigned int sync; /* protocol instance variable: Sync */
57 u16 rc; /* protocol instance variable: Rc (received send-confirm) */
58 struct sae_temporary_data *tmp;
59};
60
61int sae_set_group(struct sae_data *sae, int group);
62void sae_clear_temp_data(struct sae_data *sae);
63void sae_clear_data(struct sae_data *sae);
64
65int sae_prepare_commit(const u8 *addr1, const u8 *addr2,
66 const u8 *password, size_t password_len,
67 const char *identifier, struct sae_data *sae);
68int sae_process_commit(struct sae_data *sae);
69void sae_write_commit(struct sae_data *sae, struct wpabuf *buf,
70 const struct wpabuf *token, const char *identifier);
71u16 sae_parse_commit(struct sae_data *sae, const u8 *data, size_t len,
72 const u8 **token, size_t *token_len, int *allowed_groups);
73void sae_write_confirm(struct sae_data *sae, struct wpabuf *buf);
74int sae_check_confirm(struct sae_data *sae, const u8 *data, size_t len);
75u16 sae_group_allowed(struct sae_data *sae, int *allowed_groups, u16 group);
76const char * sae_state_txt(enum sae_state state);
77
78#endif /* SAE_H */
